{"word":"χωρίτης","slug":"χωρίτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χωρίτης</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χώρα'><el>χώρα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a countryman, rustic, boor</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>:—<a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> <el>χωρῖτις, ιδος</el>, <i>a country girl</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>one dwelling in a spot</i> or <i>country, a native</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}